data.description: This beautiful 5 bedrm/3 bathrm home has over 175K in upgrades. When you enter, you can see right through to the amazing backyard oasis but first you are greeted by the spacious two-story living room w/tons of light, an inviting staircase w/custom fireplace & wine cellar w/chiller. The open kitchen/den area has coffered ceilings, custom built ins w/FP, the kitchen has marble floors, cascading cabinets & granite counters plus eat in area. First floor also has dining room, bedroom/office plus a full bathrm w/marble tile. The oversized sliding glass doors leads to a spectacular travertine patio w/ covered porch & built in fireplace. The trex decking leads to a swim spa that has a treadmill in it as well as a hot tub area. Fenced yard. The 2nd fl continues to impress w/large bedrms & Jack & Jill bathrm, loft, primary bedrm has dual closets, a large bathrm w/separate tub & shower. Great location minutes to RiverGate Shopping Center, Lake Wylie & interstates. This home is a must see, hurry!
